To build the program:
* Prerequisites: Geant4, cmake, gcc

1: Make a build directory:
mkdir build

2: Run cmake:
cmake /path/to/G4NovoSVSC

3: Run make
make

4: To run:
./novosvsc nameofmacro.in

Test with beamN.in:
./novosvsc beamN.in

Will produce root file NovoOutput.root

*** Description of the macros ***
beamN.in:
Monoenergetic gamma point source

beam_hist.in:
Extended beta source with the energy profile of Sr-90.

vis.mac:
Visualization macro